Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:04.79,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HD8F0E8&\4c&H616484&\pos(420,389)}第四話 謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.24,0:01:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 快去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在學校過的怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.75,0:01:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然以前問她都說很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.76,0:01:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這次喜形於色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜不自禁了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是戀愛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽子 我的爽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 孩子他爸說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:19:25.42,Warning,NTP,0000,0000,0000,banner;28;0;60,翻譯:瑤瑤 老虎　校譯:キョン　時間:キョン　後期:風一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗過幸福的滋味後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿就把不知幸福滋味的時候忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨佔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但總覺得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定我現在已經把這輩子的幸福都用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 騙人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 就是眼睛很細的那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 中學時就是個問題學生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老師弄哭 還和班裡所有男生都打過架
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.61,0:02:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是幹過許多比這更厲害的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 我的眼睛可沒那麼細
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.40,0:02:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人不可貌相啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 中學就已經是百人斬了太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能滿足我的男人有100個麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.41,0:02:50.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的話就帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你們鑒定下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的光輝歷史根本不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.62,0:02:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 因為是謠言嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家的眼睛根本沒那麼細
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要比你想的細
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是假的 全是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子放的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.97,0:03:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在問你始作俑者是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子為了提高自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在利用風早同學和吉田同學還有矢野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑的我肚子痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 那裡的拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同學 吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:03:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和全班的男生都打過架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我超喜歡男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中學時代就已經是百人斬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.84,0:04:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考試的要點筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.69,0:04:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我試著做了下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能派上用處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我心懷感激的收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 矢野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去影像店借怪談的片子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話能不能給我推薦幾部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純白色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個筆記借我複印下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我替你打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:04:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能幫到別人真是很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超純白色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.55,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 真田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊 風早同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨晚真的看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小老頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞 我想快點去教室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 喝著喝著酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碗的周圍有幾個人在不斷的轉圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉啊轉轉啊轉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一個個就掉到碗裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小痞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要遲到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們現在怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫黑沼的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為和那個女孩對視
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才會不斷發生奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.11,0:06:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐她旁邊不是知道很多麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙詛咒之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只相信我自己看到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所看到黑沼是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂觀的好女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經和黑沼搞上了麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說不出話了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 真的麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 別再往下說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.06,0:06:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真 真的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太 太瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後然後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.44,0:06:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.90,0:06:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被小痞叫去聽小老頭的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.66,0:07:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額頭露出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然昨天說了獨佔這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,額頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞上了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看她了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 額頭…殘念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在感受幸福的每一天裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都心跳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.82,0:07:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家是怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起開心麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的話就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.19,0:08:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都認為周圍沒朋友是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這樣的事根本沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那一天起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.63,0:08:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我從未體會過的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.95,0:08:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填滿了內心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.91,0:08:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想好好珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像第一次收到的禮物那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同學 吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 好像最近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謠言滿天飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得變得越來越誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老爺爺打的頭破血流
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.69,0:09:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是有扶起跌倒的老爺爺這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.29,0:09:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說矢野同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做些援交的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.55,0:09:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能去做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然我們是完全不相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是說那個放出謠言的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會一下子謠言四起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有點過分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然放出那樣的謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感到周圍比以前更怕我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 詩乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.61,0:09:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.40,0:09:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近關於你的謠言變得很厲害唉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈感 詛咒什麼的謠言詩乃也已經聽說了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然誤會很難消除
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子說朋友壞話什麼的根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也不像以前那麼介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.93,0:10:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的人對我也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得貞子給人的感覺變得柔和了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.92,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼大家都說是貞子說的 貞子說的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 有人惡意中傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.71,0:10:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是對貞子還是對我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子的謠言和平常不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能交到朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫矢野和吉田對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 不是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 聽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 跟我走趟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是朋友麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺朋友是像吉田同學和矢野同學那樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每當看到她們2人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會覺得她們很喜歡對方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.83,0:11:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒那麼不自量力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我很喜歡她們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能成為朋友的那一天到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會覺得真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球部的極密練習表
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我交給龍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.49,0:11:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個傢伙都讓我覺得火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.56,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點 小千
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那句話到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還沒問過貞子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.80,0:12:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際問題是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們直接問貞子是不是朋友的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是會很微妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.59,0:12:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.28,0:12:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直笑著的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.66,0:12:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這裡坐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很認真的問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要如實的回答我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我們很喜歡你 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也喜歡我們麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:03.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其說喜歡 不如說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:04.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子 讓你困擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這幾句話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓她們明白了我的心意麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.96,0:13:29.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但矢野同學和吉田同學的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻看上去沒什麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿連我也感到很悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼方法能讓她們打起精神來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然得寸進尺到把吉田和矢野當作靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:13:58.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且連風早都隨意使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個厲害的人吶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 什麼~~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候開始我從貞子轉為幕後黑手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.61,0:14:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是但是 矢野和吉田那灰暗的傳言真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰暗的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.76,0:14:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這些才情緒低落的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們傷心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是貞子的關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯沒錯 都是因為貞子在她們周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這麼被貞子糾纏下去 絕對會人氣下滑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:51.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:15:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同學和吉田同學只是溫柔的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.30,0:15:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的對待我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只是那樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為貞子在她們周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我在她們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們受到了傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在我的身邊 風早同學不知哪一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.64,0:15:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會像矢野同學和吉田同學那樣受到傷害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.67,0:15:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了嗎 過於那個小老頭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見過的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也看見過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.42,0:15:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是不在他們身邊會好一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我不能留在他們身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.31,0:16:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 眼睛紅得好像徹夜痛哭過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野你的眼睛不也是好像熬夜一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.88,0:16:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.10,0:16:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我們的謠言是貞子放出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話我也開始迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:41.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天聽過貞子的回答以後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 至少貞子的心裡是不喜歡我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千 你問的是關於「喜歡」的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她立刻回答「喜歡」 那謠言絕對不是她傳出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們肯定會相信的 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子是不可能會散播謠言的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我百分百的相信著的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在卻不知道如果是真的我該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信謠言並不是貞子傳出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭那麼想的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛紅紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.73,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我讓你們情緒低落了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.06,0:17:55.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 貞子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貞子她是在道歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「讓你們情緒低落了」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道真的是貞子把謠言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了 別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不這樣想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了「對不起 不是喜歡」的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是那一件都讓人無法忍受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.46,0:18:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太自以為是了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為自己對貞子來說是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 以為她是真的喜歡我的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.94,0:18:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同學和吉田同學她們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠比我想像的要傷的深
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想快點找到散播謠言的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.41,0:18:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替她們澄清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢野同學和吉田同學並不是什麼靠山
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是溫柔的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把這些告訴他們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道解除誤會的辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散播謠言的那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(434,432)}聽好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓她們快點恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.27,0:19:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復成笑著的矢野同學和吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的應該是她們倆才是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.45,0:19:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:51.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且好像在躲著我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什麼傷到你的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什麼讓你討厭的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:19:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的話 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:02.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 風早同學什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算 就算風早同學真的做錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也絕對不會討厭你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼都絕對不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(423,431)}馬上考試了 你還是很輕鬆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(423,431)}就算去折騰也不會怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑沼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風早同學 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.83,0:20:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明答應過不論發生什麼都絕不避開你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我留在你的身邊會給你帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.21,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不想避開你 但是遠離你會好一些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.70,0:20:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我想在你們身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避開你們是對的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:25.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.88,0:21:25.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:36.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いかない　それが答えてなんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:36.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走 那就是回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャボン玉　飛ばそう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:39.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肥皂泡泡 飄飄浮浮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:47.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空まではきっと届かない　うちに壊れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:47.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未到達天空就破滅消散而去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:53.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いま誰知りたいの永遠じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:53.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是我們想要的永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:22:01.07,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このままずっと　いていたいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:22:01.07,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管想要永遠留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:12.34,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その空一杯の紙飛行機　暗いになって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:12.34,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空中飛滿了紙飛機
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ひとつだけ見つけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:21.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只找尋到了屬於我的唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.77,0:22:34.66,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(680,360)}第五話 決心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說很重要的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.89,0:22:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我能做的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.71,0:22:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五話 決心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡為你帶來動畫「好想告訴你」最新情報的告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.90,0:22:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩位分別是為黑沼爽子配音的能登麻美子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和為風早翔太配音的浪川大輔先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每週都在感動中配音 希望這份心意能夠傳給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.87,0:23:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這周也是緊緊張張的 繼續期待下周
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.23,0:23:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周將會有椿姬彩菜小姐的初次亮相
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很期待的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.78,0:23:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們下周見 告訴你
